{"tid":1585089,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"法律巴絲請入，懷疑被呃工傷。","createTime":"2019-09-21T12:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T04:13:51.000Z","uid":186574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"44810806a8cdc842754459edc6d407e8cbd10288","tid":1585089,"uid":186574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"有位親友做工程，請左個南亞仔第一日返工，第一次搬野(兩個人一齊)就趴係到講整親。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當日親友陪佢係公家醫院搞到凌晨，照左x光睇左醫生話無發現有乜問題，但醫生照開左7日假比佢。<br />\n<br />\n由於我親友係接公司job再自己一組人去做，類似判上判，請人返黎要上曬堂，工傷先由公司負責。但今次呢個人第一日所以未上堂，無簽約，所以依家要求我親友先賠7日糧既80%，再加醫藥費。本來都打算比完呢筆就一筆勾銷，但條友呢兩日係咁打黎話好痛，話打算自己去報勞工處。<br />\n感覺上佢7日後都會繼續話痛話盛，但又質疑唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網搵過下勞工條例，但都無乜方向。想問下意見，最差既情況可以點? 如果佢一直話痛係咪要keep住賠? 係咪請定律師都得?。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 親友好擔心，感謝各位!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133ec66c499121d4b2331462f43e7ad4cc602838","tid":1585089,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T12:35:13.000Z","msg":"[行動又無人理？] 全球最大親子抗爭活動上線啦！ <strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">#birdfoldingchallenge</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584614</a><br />\n摺一隻紙鳥，影相，放上Facebook / Twitter / Instagram，並加上hashtag #birdfoldingchallenge #929globalmarch #929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism，copy呢段文字再tag 5個朋友，就完成！</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYhkXcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYhkXcO.jpg&h=9b11593e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b2f7e3b4691ea6f50920f79584a07c3d1439ce0","tid":1585089,"uid":174013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T12:41:05.000Z","msg":"而家好多呢D職業工傷狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果醫生肯開病假紙比佢,吹佢唔漲<br />\n見過有